# Cardinal Rule: Types Flow From The Schema

ALL types, type guards, Zod schemas, and validators MUST flow from the OpenAPI schema via `pnpm sdk-codegen`.
No ad-hoc types. No broad `Record<string, unknown>`. Missing types = generator bug.

See "Cardinal Rule" in `.agent/directives/rules.md` and `.agent/directives/schema-first-execution.md`.
